        </div>
    </div>
</div>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Nota do editor</strong></h3>



<p>Quer ver mais exemplos de pop-ups? Tenha acesso imediato a mais de 100 modelos de pop-ups testados e provados (de graça).</p>



<p><a href="https://sleeknote.com/popup-examples" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Acesse nossa galeria de pop-ups</a>.</p>
</div></div>



<p>É uma sacada inteligente. Um visitante que está comparando tamanhos de colchões tem mais probabilidade de estar mais adiante na jornada do comprador do que alguém que está procurando por ajuda para dormir. Sendo assim, a Casper solicita um endereço de e-mail, em vez de feedback, e oferece seus produtos em seus e-mails de onboarding (vamos falar mais a respeito disso na 5ª parte).</p>



<div class="wp-block-group"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Ponto de ação</strong>: Se você vende tipos diferentes de produtos ( por exemplo, cosméticos como maquiagens), crie um guia de comparação para ajudar os compradores a encontrarem o produto certo para eles. Bônus se você se classificar bem nas páginas de resultados dos motores de pesquisa (SERPs).</p>
</div></div>
</div></div>



<h2 id="5"><strong>Estratégia nº5: Mostre todas as avaliações em um só lugar (BoFu)</strong></h2>



<p>Você já deve saber da importância de usar os depoimentos dos consumidores para ajudar a atrair os compradores em potencial. Mas você está mostrando esses depoimentos da melhor forma possível?</p>



<p>Sabendo da importância das avaliações num mercado competitivo, a Casper mostra todas as suas avaliações em uma só página em seu site.</p>



<p>Em primeiro lugar, ela apresenta avaliações escritas por seus clientes, incluindo o nome da pessoa, o seu local e a sua avaliação da Casper.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="532" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Casper_s-Reviews-1024x532.png" alt="19 Casper_s Reviews" class="wp-image-113815" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Casper_s-Reviews-1024x532.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Casper_s-Reviews-300x156.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Casper_s-Reviews-768x399.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Casper_s-Reviews-380x198.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Casper_s-Reviews-600x312.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Casper_s-Reviews-760x395.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Casper_s-Reviews-67x35.png 67w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Casper_s-Reviews-96x50.png 96w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Casper_s-Reviews-740x385.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Casper_s-Reviews-220x114.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Casper_s-Reviews-385x200.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Casper_s-Reviews.png 1250w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>(A Casper é 100% transparente aqui. Se você clicar em, “Ver todas as avaliações,” você pode ler tudo o que os seus clientes dizem a respeito da empresa, incluindo os clientes insatisfeitos.)</p>



<p>Abaixo de suas avaliações de clientes, você pode ler os tweets dos clientes, acrescentando ainda mais a legitimidade de suas avaliações.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="393" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Casper-Tweet-Testimonial-1024x393.png" alt="20 Casper Tweet Testimonial" class="wp-image-113819" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Casper-Tweet-Testimonial-1024x393.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Casper-Tweet-Testimonial-300x115.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Casper-Tweet-Testimonial-768x294.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Casper-Tweet-Testimonial-380x146.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Casper-Tweet-Testimonial-600x230.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Casper-Tweet-Testimonial-760x291.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Casper-Tweet-Testimonial-91x35.png 91w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Casper-Tweet-Testimonial-130x50.png 130w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Casper-Tweet-Testimonial-740x284.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Casper-Tweet-Testimonial-220x84.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Casper-Tweet-Testimonial-385x148.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Casper-Tweet-Testimonial.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Por fim, a Casper adicionou uma terceira camada de prova social: as medalhas de mídia e as menções de imprensa.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="646" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Casper_s-Media-Mentions-1024x646.png" alt="21 Casper_s Media Mentions" class="wp-image-113823" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Casper_s-Media-Mentions-1024x646.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Casper_s-Media-Mentions-300x189.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Casper_s-Media-Mentions-768x485.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Casper_s-Media-Mentions-1536x969.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Casper_s-Media-Mentions-380x240.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Casper_s-Media-Mentions-600x379.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Casper_s-Media-Mentions-760x479.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Casper_s-Media-Mentions-1440x909.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Casper_s-Media-Mentions-55x35.png 55w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Casper_s-Media-Mentions-79x50.png 79w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Casper_s-Media-Mentions-740x467.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Casper_s-Media-Mentions-220x139.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Casper_s-Media-Mentions-385x243.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Casper_s-Media-Mentions.png 1585w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Há um motivo pelo qual a Casper se esforçou bastante para otimizar a sua página de avaliações e discutiremos por que na 5ª parte: Estratégia nº2.</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Ponto de ação</strong>: É comum que as lojas online exibam suas avaliações em sites de terceiros. Mas isso nem sempre quer dizer que é uma boa prática. Leve suas melhores avaliações e destaque-as em uma página em seu site para que você tenha mais controle sobre como você divulga seu negócio.&nbsp;</p>
</div></div>



<h2><strong>3ª parte: Construção de links</strong></h2>



<p>Na data em que isto foi escrito, a Casper possui 148 mil backlinks de 5,54 mil domínios de referência.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="152" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-Casper_s-Backlinks-1024x152.png" alt="22 Casper_s Backlinks" class="wp-image-113827" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-Casper_s-Backlinks-1024x152.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-Casper_s-Backlinks-300x44.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-Casper_s-Backlinks-768x114.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-Casper_s-Backlinks-1536x227.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-Casper_s-Backlinks-380x56.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-Casper_s-Backlinks-600x89.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-Casper_s-Backlinks-760x113.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-Casper_s-Backlinks-1440x213.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-Casper_s-Backlinks-180x27.png 180w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-Casper_s-Backlinks-250x37.png 250w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-Casper_s-Backlinks-740x110.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-Casper_s-Backlinks-220x33.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-Casper_s-Backlinks-385x57.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-Casper_s-Backlinks.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Isso é impressionante, mas a não ser que você tenha um orçamento de marketing multimilionário, poucas de suas estratégias de construção de links podem ser replicadas (se você está curioso para saber, eu incluí minhas três favoritas no recurso bônus).</p>



<p>Sendo assim, em vez de explorar o que não pode ser replicado, eu quero lhe mostrar três formas não convencionais que a Casper utiliza para construir seus links e como você também pode fazer isso.&nbsp;</p>



<h2 id="6"><strong>Estratégia nº6: Crie links .edu white-hat com o “Método CSD”</strong></h2>



<p>Se você sabe alguma coisa sobre o link building, você já deve saber que ter links .edu é o melhor que você pode conseguir. Eles trazem MUITO Page Rank (classificação de página), mas também são difíceis de conseguir. A não ser, claro, que você tenha um método especial&#8230;</p>



<p>Dê uma olhada nos domínios de referência da Casper.</p>



<p>Se refinamos a busca, podemos ver que eles construíram doze links .edu do-follow utilizando, em minhas palavras, a estratégia dos descontos para alunos (CSD).&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="536" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-Education-Links-to-Casper-1024x536.png" alt="23 Education Links to Casper" class="wp-image-113831" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-Education-Links-to-Casper-1024x536.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-Education-Links-to-Casper-300x157.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-Education-Links-to-Casper-768x402.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-Education-Links-to-Casper-1536x804.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-Education-Links-to-Casper-380x199.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-Education-Links-to-Casper-600x314.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-Education-Links-to-Casper-760x398.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-Education-Links-to-Casper-1440x754.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-Education-Links-to-Casper-67x35.png 67w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-Education-Links-to-Casper-95x50.png 95w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-Education-Links-to-Casper-740x388.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-Education-Links-to-Casper-220x115.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-Education-Links-to-Casper-385x202.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-Education-Links-to-Casper.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Então, o que a Casper está fazendo para construir estes links?&nbsp;</p>



<p>Ela está inserindo seu produto nas vidas de um público que pode beneficiá-la:</p>



<p><em>Os alunos.</em></p>



<p>Dê uma olhada nesta página da California State University, Northridge (CSUN):</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="640" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Link-from-CSUN-1024x640.png" alt="24 Link from CSUN" class="wp-image-113835" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Link-from-CSUN-1024x640.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Link-from-CSUN-300x187.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Link-from-CSUN-768x480.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Link-from-CSUN-1536x960.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Link-from-CSUN-380x237.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Link-from-CSUN-600x375.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Link-from-CSUN-760x475.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Link-from-CSUN-1440x900.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Link-from-CSUN-56x35.png 56w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Link-from-CSUN-80x50.png 80w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Link-from-CSUN-740x462.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Link-from-CSUN-220x137.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Link-from-CSUN-385x241.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Link-from-CSUN.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Nela, os alunos podem obter descontos para uma variedade de produtos e serviços incluindo roupas, seguros—e colchões.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="149" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Casper-Discount-Code-1024x149.png" alt="25 Casper Discount Code" class="wp-image-113839" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Casper-Discount-Code-1024x149.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Casper-Discount-Code-300x44.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Casper-Discount-Code-768x112.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Casper-Discount-Code-1536x223.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Casper-Discount-Code-380x55.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Casper-Discount-Code-600x87.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Casper-Discount-Code-760x111.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Casper-Discount-Code-1440x209.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Casper-Discount-Code-180x26.png 180w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Casper-Discount-Code-250x36.png 250w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Casper-Discount-Code-740x108.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Casper-Discount-Code-220x32.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Casper-Discount-Code-385x56.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Casper-Discount-Code.png 1650w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Concidência? Talvez. Mas talvez não.</p>



<p>Aqui vai outro exemplo da State University of New York, mais uma vez, com uma página de descontos para produtos e serviços para os alunos.</p>



